          <h1>Local Races</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content_box box_1">
          <p>
            Looking to fuel your competitive spirit? Maybe you just want some extra motivation to push your workouts a bit harder? Then seriously consider signing up for some local races. There are not nearly as intimidating as you might think. They are a great way to feed into the local cycling community and meet some great people at the same time. You can see whats happening through the link below.
          </p>
          <div class="raceReg">
              <a href="https://www.bikereg.com/" target="_blank"><img class="sm_img" src="/images/logos/bikereg_2block.png" alt="BikeReg race registration"/></a>
