              <p class="text_clr2">Lead one (or more!) group ride (mountain or road or Rootbeer Ride) per year.</p>
              <p class="text_clr1">Be ambassadors for our shop! Talk us up, tag us on social media, be a responsible rider</p>
              <p class="text_clr2">Follow IMBA's <a href="https://www.imba.com/ride/imba-rules-of-the-trail" target="_blank">rules of the trail</a>, and be the all-around cool person that you already are.</p>
